name: qwen2-math
description: Qwen2 Math is a series of specialized math language models built upon the Qwen2 LLMs, which significantly outperforms the mathematical capabilities of open-source models and even closed-source models (e.g., GPT4o).
readme_html:
Qwen2 Math features 3 model sizes (1.5B, 7B, and 72B) each with a base model, for completion, few-shot inference, and fine-tuning, and an instruct model for chatting.

References:

  • Qwen 2 Math Blog Post
  • GitHub Repository
  • Hugging Face
